Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界各地的地殼變動漸趨劇烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型Aquarion被解除封印的影響現已波及全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又無法知悉阿馬塔他們的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能用預備機體前往Altair把它奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是次元門不開我們還能有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來給次元空間開個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是偶然獲得的能力 加上那時有修雷特幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此 我還是成功過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不試一下 迄今為止我都是為了什麼在挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去吧 理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪·W·霍爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的力量上孤注一擲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要妨礙我嗎 太陽之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是確保真正的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開對核心單元的直接攻擊 只剝奪其戰鬥能力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲這傢伙 少瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是太陽之翼的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能瞬間摧毀GNIS機體的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就加倍奉還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是反彈攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就再次逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆轉的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的反彈攻擊正逐漸被抵消
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲 我死也不會把臭女人交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼如此執著於這個Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是我的…只屬於我的臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲大人 我來支援您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Abductor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mix 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair的未來與出雲大人同在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定要平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是男生的合體真是久違了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要到達目標地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 全是男生的殺伐合體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這樣的合體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是激情澎湃的壯士合體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUARION GEPART
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你的身體變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定會去迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前說過的吧 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞是…洞是為了連接世界而開啟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會連通你所身處的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 在你的心房也開一個大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個足以容下我的大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擬次元門出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 小子們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有誰在呼喚我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我的名字叫Mi·xy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 坐在上面的是Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘖 可惡的出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝相反方向起飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUARION GEPART
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到一下子就碰上了激戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩台Abductor和神話型Aquarion 都是誰在操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎 是怪炎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會和這個傢伙在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Mix的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩台Abductor企圖要擄走御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔和修雷特怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和阿馬塔失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特…已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在次元的狹縫中奏響了最後的樂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 那時候的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要阻礙出雲大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想帶你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我回去?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想起來吧 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起我 想起我安迪·W·霍爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話令我不快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清局勢吧 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道不想拯救Altair嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和星球的未來沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想和臭女人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算與全世界為敵 我也不會放開臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mix Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了一個Igler…一個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喚我的聲音是從那裡傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球 大地 和沉睡著的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今 這一切即將要甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼的復活是一柄雙刃劍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會化為分割世界的力量 還是連接世界的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間補填
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從剛才開始就在重複同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直重複下去 直至將Mix擁入懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挖洞 Mix來填
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是通過這樣互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷重複這種無謂之舉的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得似曾相識
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 終於能見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初明明就拋棄了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我一直以來是以怎樣的心情生活的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而到了現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不奢求你的原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我希望你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當初拋棄你的苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及你爸爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的爸爸不是地球上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他名叫出雲·神呂木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Altair的最高領導人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了給夏娃的詛咒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給糾纏著Rare·Igler的悲劇畫上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸身負帶回能承受次元轉移的女性的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到了地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我還是個演員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她救了因系統故障而迫降到Vega的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快我就察覺到艾麗西亞就是我們所需要的Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比那更短的時間內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們相互吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法嘲笑神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾經因為一個女人而企圖背叛Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向高層部門隱瞞了她的存在並返回了Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這沒能瞞過未影的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數年後 當他再次出現的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 從出雲那裡聽說了夏娃的詛咒之後 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不知道Rare·Igler在那邊會遭到何種對待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能幫到你的話 我沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了要不要帶你一起去而猶豫了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更擔心你在未知的星球上會遇到什麼危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這竟然會演變成如此長久的分離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拋棄了你是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要拯救深愛的人的星球 拯救他所愛的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在憎恨著你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我憎恨的是那時候只能眼睜睜看著一切發生的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著自己所愛的人的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有 而我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣而已 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你糾纏夠了吧 出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓艾麗西亞白白犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型Aquarion在戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在交戰的是出雲和另一個你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說神樂?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的母親奧莉莎所建造的Iron C
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的線?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair的全部能量都漸漸匯聚到Afura Gnis身上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母星總力戰炮（Altair Cannon）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒就是Altair所擁有的力量本身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那僅僅是警告而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不交出真正的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次我將會全力發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的 創聖的無限拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股力量…未影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你這傢伙搞的鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聽說了你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我去艾麗西亞的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有資格請求你原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…把你的母親從你身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:20:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜉蝣?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候曾經見過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為沒有了雌性 應該早已絕種了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在還…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是337區
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Iron C故障頻發的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…Iron C本身就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親般的大地 大地的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來豐收之恩澤的大地 象徵著女性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女和男 陰和陽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為有這兩極 森羅萬象的一切秩序才得以維持
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人和大地亦然 星球和宇宙亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.74,0:22:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Iron C是從星球的大地攝取出能量的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同時也可能因此奪去了星球母性的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那樣的話 Iron C就是一切的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.91,0:22:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一生豈不是全都白費了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.35,0:22:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點 我們好不容易才見到面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有白費
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一生絕對沒有白費
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你把阿馬塔帶到了這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子肯定會拯救兩個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 你是我們相愛的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 你也去愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去愛那個你比任何人都要珍視的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.96,0:24:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命運中的臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.07,0:24:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道你真正的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.34,0:24:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 我愛你 希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要緊抱住你的一切
