Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:55.89,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}降臨到我的庭院來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:23:01.50,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即使思念無法傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.68,0:23:07.06,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}也能使兩人變得堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:12.77,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}Aquaria Aquaria
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:18.97,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}有多少晚我仰望星座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:24.83,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}讓思緒馳騁於未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:30.25,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}直至安睡在你懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:33.39,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}思緒馳騁於未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:36.95,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}直至其重歸安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:43.67,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}快越過漆黑的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:51.73,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}前來迎接我吧
